    "Establishing and developing the green finance pilot zone can be important in promoting the dual-carbon goal.",
    "On June 14, 2017, China selected eight regions in five provinces, namely, Zhejiang, Jiangxi, Guangdong, Guizhou, and Xinjiang, to build green finance reform and innovation pilot zones.",
