    "Column (14) in Table 6 shows that the estimation coefficient of the core explanatory variable is still significantly positive.",
    "In 2019, the scope of the green finance reform pilot zone was further expanded, and Lanzhou New Area in Gansu Province was approved as the ninth green finance reform and innovation pilot zone."
